descriptionHtml:
Download the file and place the Batch file in your Skyrim folder
open the console in game and type "bat mwizard"

Gives the ultimate wizard template,
Gives multiple staffs including the Staff of Magnus,
Gives the Archmage's Robes with matching shoes ring and circlet,
Gives all ingredients for tasting to get alchemy knowledge,
Gives all enchantments through items,
Gives 1000000000 gold,
Gives 1000000000 lockpicks,
Gives all spells,
Gives all shouts,
author: IceflameV
